### Get Database Statistics
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### List All Tables
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Count Users
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables/users/count
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### View Sample Users
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables/users/sample?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### View Sample Students
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables/students/sample?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### View Sample Courses
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables/courses/sample?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### View Sample Enrollments
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables/enrollments/sample?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### View Sample Grades
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables/grades/sample?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### View Sample Invoices
GET https://academic-portal-api.onrender.com/api/v1/admin/db/tables/invoices/sample?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###
# To use these requests:
# 1. Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code
# 2. Login as admin via /docs to get your JWT token
# 3. Replace YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE with your actual token
# 4. Click "Send Request" above each request
